Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Panama treaty agreed
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040brvq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 23 Apr 1978
Casting vote saves Panama treaty after 13 years of negotiation over future of the canal. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less